---
import Hero from "@/common/components/Hero.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Computer Science">
    <Hero 
    title="Mathematics (B.Sc.)" 
    subtitle="Department of Mathematics and Computer Science"
    />

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto gap-5 md:gap-10 mb-20 p-5">
        <aside class="col-span-1">
            <nav>
                <ul class="bg-gray-100 font-kanit text-xl grid">
                    <a href="academics" class="p-5 ">Academics</a>
                    <a class="p-5 e" href="apply">Apply</a>
                    <a class="p-5 border-l-8 border-yellow-400 underline decoration-4 decoration-yellow-400 bg-slate-900 text-white" href="opportunities">Opportunities</a>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </aside>
        <main class="md:col-span-3 my-5 grid space-y-5 font-sarabun">
            <h2 class="text-5xl font-kanit font-semibold">Opportunities</h2>
            <p>There is a wide range of career opportunities available. For examples, researchers or academics; teachers
                or professors in academic institutions; mathematicians; statisticians; insurance mathematicians; insurance 
                mathematics personnels; financial analysts in securities firms and financial institutions; financial and banking 
                personnels; data scientists or data analysts. Moreover, graduate studies in various areas are ones of the 
                options.</p>
        </main>
    </div>


</BaseLayout>